SAP Ariba – End Users of Production Services 

“In an enterprise procurement platform like SAP Ariba, our production services supported a wide range of internal B2B stakeholders and external enterprise users.

### 1. External Enterprise Users

* Procurement managers
* Buyers and suppliers
* Vendor administrators and contract managers
* Users executing sourcing events, contracts, POs, invoices, and supplier collaboration
* Global organizations relying on Ariba for procure-to-pay (P2P) operations

### 2. Internal Stakeholders

* Engineering, QA, and product teams working on core procurement modules
* Customer success and support teams using internal dashboards
* Integration teams managing SAP ECC/S4 interfaces
* Compliance, audit, and InfoSec teams

My responsibility was to maintain the reliability, compliance, uptime, and performance of procurement services that directly impacted supplier onboarding, contract workflows, PO generation, and invoicing.”